window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>This collection of short ghost stories includes some of the best-known classics in the genre, as well as some that may be new to ghost story fans. Includes: ”The Damned Thing by Ambrose Bierce, ”The Empty House\" by Algernon Blackwood, ”The Consequences\" by Willa Cather, ”How It Happened\" by Sir Arthur Conan Doyle, ”A Ghost\" by Guy De Maupassant, ”The Shell of Sense\" by Olivia Howard Dunbar, ”Ligeia\" by Edgar Allen Poe, ”The Signal-Man\" by Charles Dickens, ”The Secret of the Growing Gold\" by Bram Stoker, ”The Fullness of Life\" by Edith Wharton, ”An Old Woman's Tale\" by Nathaniel Hawthorne, ”Playing with Fire\" by Sir Arthur Conan Doyle, ”Narrative of the Ghost of the Hand\" by J. Sheridan Le Fanu; ”The Facts in the Case of M. Valdemar\" by Edgar Allan Poe; ”My Platonic Sweetheart\" by Mark Twain; and ”The Bold Dragoon (or The Adventure of My Grandfather)\" by Washington Irving.</p>"; 
